en klinischen Erfahrung des Autors. Das Buch eignet sich durch den Praxisbezug hervorragend zum Selbststudium sowie für den praktischen Unterricht an Universitäten.  aThis book offers a comprehensive introduction to gynecological diagnosis in private and hospital practice. A focus is placed on medical history screening, the clinical examination, and vaginal ultrasound testing, which provide indication for further diagnostic testing with different examination techniques.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Dez 2019) 4aDidaktik der Frauenheilkunde. 4agynäkologische Anamnese. 4agynäkologische Diagnostik. 4agynäkologische Untersuchung. 7aMEDICAL / Gynecology & Obstetrics.2bisacsh1 aEbert, Andreas D., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2018z9783110603200oZDB-23-DPM0 cEPUBz97831104090860 cprintz978311037863440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110409017423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110409017.jpg  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA1ALL  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DPMb2018